text.tspan: Fig 1: Build and Run AWS Examples as-is, using AWS XSim flow
- Does single-word 'poke' and 'peek' into the OCL port (AXI4-Lite.32.32)
- Invokes ddr_init() to initialize the DDRs
- Does a DMA copy to/from each of the DDRs
Note: cannot use Verilator: non-synthesizable stuff in SH-BFM + encrypted IP.
Can use XSIM, ModelSim, VCS, Cadence Sim
